BREAKFLOORZM_FIXED

This is the second release of breakfloorzm.
This release fixes various bugs and graphical glitches with the original.
It also has been further optimized for better FPS and less lag.
The map also now works on Linux servers.

The entire point of this remake is that users are automatically teleported back to the top of the map if they fall into the pit below the breakable floor. This way, users don't need to type or bind !ztele or any of that, and the gameplay will therefore be much better. Of course, there will also be less chat and mic spam as a result.

Credit for the original breakfloor goes to tstar.
This map was made for ZombieMod breakfloor servers.
It was also originally a request by a ZM fan.

Enjoy. =D
Comments, assessments, and stamps are more than welcome.
Just be sure to try out the map!

Regards,
£cho
Official FPSBanana ZombieMod Representative

~~~BREAKFLOORZM~~~
This map was a request.

This is a remake of the popular map "breakfloor". Normally, you keep shooting blocks of metal until you fall into a pit to your doom. However, there's been a couple changes to the map for ZM integration. They are as follows:

- Retextured, a sort of "dust" theme.
- Added a teleport at the bottom of the pit so users are returned to the top if they fall. They are returned to the middle area inbetween the two spawn areas.
- Made boxes so players can jump on them and get to the middle area.
- Allowed access to the walls of the map so that players can walk on them and get there via the stairs I've added.

These changes are quite simple, but they can really help the people wishing to make a good 24/7 ZombieMod breakfloor server. So, I suggest unless you hate breakfloor maps, that you download this map and try it out.

==========
FINAL has been released:

- Retextured again to give more of a "dust2" feel.
- Maximum optimization for the least amount of FPS loss and lag possible.
- Fixed teleportation issues that may occur when falling down the shoot.
- Made bsp filesize smaller for easy downloading.
- Fixed buyzone problems.
- Fixed lighting issues.

SCREENSHOTS ARE NOW UP-TO-DATE
Screenshots are displaying breakfloorzm_final.
==========

Thanks for downloading!
Regards,

Grey-Echo (£cho)
FPSBanana ZombieMod Representative

During the Cold War II, an atlantic island is known to possess a high mortal virus. A special team of military as civilians is sent to get a sample of the virus and destroy the rest, but of member of their team got infected. Human's Objective: Get out of the island before the nuke arrives and prevent any further infections. Zombie's Objective: Infect all humans and spread the infection around the world. Other Notes: There is one rescue aircraft at the surface. Don't try to leave the island swimming.
